# Backend API base URL (required for production build; dev uses Vite proxy to /api)
# Production (GCP Cloud Run): set to your Cloud Run URL + /api before npm run build
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR_SERVICE-xxx.run.app/api
#
# Local dev: leave unset to use /api (proxied by vite.config.ts to http://localhost:5000)
# E2E without proxy: VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
#
# Optional: DeepSeek API key for aptitude/coding/report (if not using backend /api/deepseek/token)
# VITE_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
